{"tid":1404570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毅進協會: 譴責暴徒是「害怕曝光與蟑螂無異」","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:23:22.000Z","uid":209024,"like":17,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"6baad5089fc3477c185695e8526f971bb99f02ec","tid":1404570,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"黃大仙及油尖旺昨晚發生激烈警民衝突，警察隊員佐級協會強烈譴責有關暴力及破壞行為，並形容暴徒是「害怕曝光與蟑螂無異」。<br />\n<br />\n協會聲明指出，從網上片段可見，有人刻意換衣服打扮成附近居民，在黃大仙製造事端及暴力衝擊警察，有人在尖沙咀將國旗拆下及拋到海面，掛上有宣揚港獨的旗幟，明目張膽侮辱國家及挑戰國家主權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n協會表示，有人開始肆意在人口稠密的鬧市縱火及使用汽油彈，一旦發生火災後果不堪設想，屬於非常嚴重的罪行，呼籲停止有關行為。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472431-20190804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472431-20190804.htm&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e8bc1250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472431-20190804.htm&h=9b7a3137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472431-20190804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a779a6bf2ec67c90444d93d6dd36322734a6dcb","tid":1404570,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a159745ed17f30cee78e7c58c4a4aafdacdc8859","tid":1404570,"uid":50457,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"福利會變左政府代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80a0094d3a3b6f237a611434567bfaeab432c7c","tid":1404570,"uid":256689,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"講緊自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=